{"tid":39502,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"又被叫錯名　田少：讚就田北俊、鬧就田北辰啦","createTime":"2016-12-14T15:09:23.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-15T05:56:26.000Z","uid":11001,"like":15,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"91af74e0b1085c6f5778e3fbfbc26cb162f54eb1","tid":39502,"uid":11001,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-14T15:09:23.000Z","msg":"自由黨榮譽主席田北俊（田少）今朝上商台《在晴朗的一天出發》做嘉賓，主持陳志雲就叫另一個主持郭志仁介紹田北俊出場，話要睇吓佢會唔會講錯田少個名，咁郭志仁就梗係無講錯啦，仲搞笑咁話田少係節目客席主持添。<br />\n<br />\n不過田少就搲晒頭，問佢哋點解無啦啦會講錯佢個名，陳志雲就解話，因為田少同細佬田二少、新民黨田北辰個名差一個字，好易叫錯，<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">田少聞言即刻話：「最好讚就用田北俊啦，鬧就用田北辰啦，好嘛？」</span></span>成班主持即刻哄堂大笑。唔知田少咁講，田二少會唔會唔開心呢？<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://news.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20161214/s00001/1481689695754\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20161214%2Fs00001%2F1481689695754&d=Z33%2F7%2BY5kcTcl6mDTHEi8XvMcj1OveTHk6NUHU39nRk%3D&h=7062e2b2\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20161214%2Fs00001%2F1481689695754&h=6343d4a4\" target=\"_blank\">http://news.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20161214/s00001/1481689695754</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2e8cb1cb53096cdd3acdf3f086098651c49840f1","tid":39502,"uid":2110,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-14T15:11:31.000Z","msg":"其實都幾肯定好多人分唔清佢2兄弟而投錯票"},{"pid":"e15de8039570b5408d8988318248013bfad6791b","tid":39502,"uid":57705,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-14T15:13:38.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"bdf7fdde32b1366c5193722572ede7ff4358d25e","tid":39502,"uid":22858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-14T15:14:48.000Z","msg":